OL,3,CReform's big wins in England's local
OL,4,Celections as spectre of Brexit lives on
OL,6,FWords by ITV News Election Analyst
OL,7,FColin Rallings
OL,9,FThe English local election results so
OL,10,Ffar bear out most of the predictions
OL,11,Fmade before polling day.
OL,13,FThe detail of the competition between
OL,14,Fthe parties varies across the country,
OL,15,Fbut the overall pattern is clear.
OL,17,FReform UK is doing very well, if
OL,18,Fperhaps falling short of sweeping all
OL,19,Fbefore it.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
