OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1778270754
OL,3,CReform's big wins in England's local
OL,4,Celections as spectre of Brexit lives on
OL,6,FThere are also signs of solid progress
OL,7,Fby the Greens, with the Liberal
OL,8,FDemocrats advancing in the limited
OL,9,Fareas of the country it has begun to
OL,10,Fmake its own.
OL,12,FBy contrast, and for the second year
OL,13,Fin succession, a majority of the
OL,14,Felectorate has turned against the two
OL,15,Ftraditional parties which together
OL,16,Fhave been in power since the Second
OL,17,FWorld War.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
