OL,3,CReform's big wins in England's local
OL,4,Celections as spectre of Brexit lives on
OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FReform is taking seats from Labour in
OL,12,Fmany urban areas from Plymouth in the
OL,13,Fsouth, to Salford and Wigan in the
OL,14,Fnorth.
OL,16,FThat pattern is certain to be
OL,17,Freinforced as the day progresses.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
