OL,3,CReform's big wins in England's local
OL,4,Celections as spectre of Brexit lives on
OL,6,FIt has the Conservatives in its sights
OL,7,Fin the county elections, where results
OL,8,Fmirror those last year, when the
OL,9,FTories lost control of every county
OL,10,Fthey were defending.
OL,12,FEssex looks certain to fall direct to
OL,13,FFarage's party as Kent did last year;
OL,14,Fin Hampshire, on the other hand, the
OL,15,FConservatives have suffered losses to
OL,16,Fboth Reform and the Liberal Democrats.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
