OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1778270754
OL,3,CReform's big wins in England's local
OL,4,Celections as spectre of Brexit lives on
OL,6,FGains for such seemingly opposed
OL,7,Fparties are indicative of the
OL,8,Ffragmentation of the party system
OL,9,Fwhich it itself often reflects local
OL,10,Fdemography and no longer involves a
OL,11,Fstraight exchange of votes between
OL,12,FLabour and the Conservatives as
OL,13,Fhappened in the past.
OL,15,FThe Conservatives do retain support in
OL,16,Fsome more affluent and rural areas
OL,17,Fwhere the Liberal Democrats pose the
OL,18,Fgreatest challenge.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
