OL,3,CReform's big wins in England's local
OL,4,Celections as spectre of Brexit lives on
OL,6,FLabour is losing seats to Reform, but
OL,7,Fmany of those losses have been
OL,8,Fmagnified by the party also shedding
OL,9,Fvotes to its left, in particular to
OL,10,Fthe Greens.
OL,12,FLondon, where there have been
OL,13,Fwholesale borough elections, reflects
OL,14,Fthe new politics.
OL,16,FIn Havering, for example, bordering
OL,17,FEssex and where one of the local
OL,18,FConservative MPs recently defected to
OL,19,FReform, Reform has gained almost 40
OL,20,Fseats and now sits on a large majority.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1778270754
OL,3,CReform's big wins in England's local
OL,4,Celections as spectre of Brexit lives on
OL,6,FOn the other side of the capital in
OL,7,FEaling and in Hammersmith and Fulham,
OL,8,FLabour has lost seats but retained
OL,9,Fcontrol of the councils with Reform
OL,10,Fnowhere to be seen.
OL,12,FThe Conservatives have won back the
OL,13,Ftotemic council of Westminster and
OL,14,Fdeprived Labour of its majority in
OL,15,FWandsworth.
OL,17,FThe figures suggest, however, that the
OL,18,FLabour vote has fallen back and
OL,19,Ffragmented rather than the
OL,20,FConservatives picking up support.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1778270754
OL,3,CReform's big wins in England's local
OL,4,Celections as spectre of Brexit lives on
OL,6,FThe Lib Dems have also made progress
OL,7,Fin boroughs they already controlled
OL,8,Flike Richmond upon Thames and Sutton.
OL,10,FIn Richmond, where the Greens
OL,11,Fbenefited from a pact with the Liberal
OL,12,FDemocrats four years ago, they were
OL,13,Fwiped out in a council which now only
OL,14,Fhas only Liberal Democrat councillors.
OL,16,FWhat still underpins a lot of this,
OL,17,Ften years after the event, is the
OL,18,Fspectre of Brexit.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
