OL,3,CReform's big wins in England's local
OL,4,Celections as spectre of Brexit lives on
OL,6,FLeave supporting areas are those most
OL,7,Fprone to register gains for Reform and
OL,8,Falso show signs of a rise in usual
OL,9,Fturnout levels as occurred in 2016; in
OL,10,Fplaces which voted to remain in the
OL,11,FEU, the party still struggles.
OL,13,FThe new multi-party system can also
OL,14,Fmagnify the benefit for those who get
OL,15,Fout in front.
OL,17,FKeir Starmer won his stonking 172 seat
OL,18,Fmajority at the 2024 general election
OL,19,Fwith just 34% of the national vote.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
